How it works (in text based diagrams)


                             |Broadcaster
WWW Server <-----------------|Streamer
             get application |Viewer



Map Server <----------- Broadcaster
             registers

Map Server <----------- Streamer
             registers

Map Server <----------- Viewer
             registers


Map Server -------> Streamer --------> Broadcaster
            tells             to use

Map Server -------> Viewer --------> Broadcaster
            tells           to use



Streamer ------> Signaling Server ---------------> Broadcaster
          uses                     to connect to

Viewer ------> Signaling Server ---------------> Broadcaster ----------> Streamer
        uses                     to connect to                to watch